lead_paragraph: The Asia swing is the rare trip where Patrick Reed's wife doesn't accompany him. She stayed in Houston because they're finally moving into their new house at The Woodlands.

headline.print_headline: American Golfer Patrick Reed Has Game, Loves to Travel
